{"tid":103042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「微信」識仔遇淫狼　女子慘遭施暴","createTime":"2017-02-01T05:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T07:06:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64e5659cda64b1ba2552ea9731d05a039df6bd90","tid":103042,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"女子墮微信交友陷阱遭強姦！一名29歲女子，早前透過微信結識一名年約37歲男子。雙方十分投契，有人提出於新春期間，在香港仔鴨脷洲徑一單位見面。 <br />\n<br />\n惟兩人見面後，有人霸王硬上弓，向女子施暴。事主受辱後離開現場。至昨晚9時許，自行往瑪麗醫院治理，並報警求助。 <br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查後，列作強姦案，由西區警區刑事調查隊跟進，正設法追緝淫狼歸案。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/mobile/bkn-20170201020930330-0201_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170201020930330-0201_00822_001.html&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9a846b9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/mobile/bkn-20170201020930330-0201_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4f2950a09348ad04406ea8b9cb30f2f9dc8c5013","tid":103042,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"條女29歲，除非係低能，否則都係勞資糾紛居多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58129bccb54458f5bf2d0105ebb20f452036205d","tid":103042,"uid":69751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"點會上單位見面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5909cdb48f88ec2827a13f194de26e350075be17","tid":103042,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"321ac30dbaf99d37b811e11ef0fa88540185e224","tid":103042,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:29:46.000Z","msg":"透過微信結識<br />\n<br />\n完<